Description: pandoc-latex-environmentlatex-environment
        =========================================
        
        `Build
        Status <https://travis-ci.org/chdemko/pandoc-latex-environment/branches>`__
        `Coveralls <https://coveralls.io/github/chdemko/pandoc-latex-environment?branch=1.1.2>`__
