        `PyPI version <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-environment/>`__
        `PyPI
        format <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-environment/1.1.2/>`__
        `License <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chdemko/pandoc-latex-environment/1.1.2/LICENSE>`__
        `Downloads <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-environment/>`__
